reviewText: The video is great for a growing worship leader who wants his team to do the best with what God has blessed them with.

This is a great video for anybody looking for tips, knowledge, or possibly building a worship for your team. I have been singing for 10 years and found this DVD to be very helpful for me and a lot of what I learned I now share a lot with my team. It is definitely a great tool to have in your resource library.
